   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>GROUP 3</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>MAIN POINTS OF THE GOSPEL Subject Two Hundred Twenty-seven GOD Scripture: Rom 1:19-20; Acts 14:15-18; 17:24-29 The creation of the universe proves the existence of God The order of the universe proves the existence of God The biological structure of man proves the existence of God The psychological structure of man proves the existence of God Subject Two Hundred Twenty-eight THE DEVIL Scripture: John 8:44; 1 John 5:19; 3:8 Everything in the universe has its opposite Positive and negative, up and down, good and evil, true and false, are opposites.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>White and black, light and darkness, heaven and earth, are also opposites.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Hence, as there is a God, there must also be a Devil.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>All the contradictions in the universe come from this opposition between God and the Devil Since there exists both God and the Devil, a conflict occurs.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>All the opposite pairs such as good and evil, light and darkness, white and black, true and false, are contradictions existing in the universe.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>All the tragedies and miseries in the universe originate from the Devil Since there is not only God but also the Devil, there appear not only bright, good, and happy things, but also dark, evil, and miserable things.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>All the dark, evil, and miserable things come from the Devil.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>All the sins of man come from the Devil No one sins voluntarily and willingly, but everyone sins because he cannot help it.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>This is because the whole world lies in the hand of the Devil.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>The Devil, which is Satan, is the enemy of God The existence of falsehood proves the existence of truth in the same way that the existence of forged bank notes proves that there are genuine ones.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>The existence of a Devil proves the existence of God.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Subject Two Hundred Twenty-nine MAN Scripture: Gen 1:26-27; 1 John 3:8a; Rom 3:10-12; Heb 9:27; Rev 20:11-15 Man is made by God and for God</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Man was innocent in his original state.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Man followed after Satan</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>By this he became corrupted and forsook God.</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>Man sinned The end of man s sin is death</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>After death there is judgment, and after judgment, there is the lake of fire.</S>
   </TEXT>
